    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Joseba ta Kehnixa\nJoranja Meita/Akasijus Mahfa.\nnehme Joasu Akasijus Dehlu/\nun pasagge to no ta Kehnixa\nBehrneem/ kas nokauti ktua/\nlihds ar winna Eminnu gullamâ\nRainbari/ un tee apſlehpe winnu\npreekſch Atalijas/ ka tas ne tappe nokauts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch bija ar tahs ta\nKUNGA Namunâ feſchus Gad-\ndus apflehpts/ un Atalija waldirja pahr to Semmi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
