    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Kapteines darpehz wiſſu/ ko tas Preesteris jadus teem bij pawchlejs/ un katrs nehme ſawus Wihrukam Swehdeenâ Kahrtâ jastahun kas no Swehdeenâs Kahratſtahjahs/ un nahze pee to Puſteri Jojadu.\n"
    },
