      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Preesteris de-teem Kapteinehm Schkehpus preekſchturranas Brukunas/ tam Kehnixam Dahwidain pderrejufchas/ un eekſch ta KuGA Namuna bija.\n"
